Wesog Search is an application that allows users to search editorial and creative images online at stock photography agencies and news agencies.

If you are a graphic editor or journalist looking for a solution to find images or verify their authorship, this is your application.

How does Wesog Search work?
Once the plugin is installed, you can search for the source of the image you need or the most similar one within all the collections of our associates.

Why use Wesog Search?

Reduces search times
With just one click, our advanced artificial intelligence search engine will show you the source image or the most semantically similar images. Say goodbye to conducting multiple searches in different image banks.

Identification of editorial images
Our search engine is capable of identifying the context, character, and place of an editorial image. This allows us to provide good results in an efficient and effective manner.

Source of inspiration
With Wesog Search, you can use an image as a starting point and instantly discover similar images across all our partners. This efficiency not only saves time but also ensures a higher quality in the images you select.

Authenticity and copyright protection
Our tool identifies the original source of the images, allowing you to verify their authenticity and assists in the protection of copyright.
